{"tid":1781153,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"行咇已經變左係便衣甴行","createTime":"2019-12-13T02:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T03:58:52.000Z","uid":236646,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac22ea9746c7e3e8db5a5f1a92f0b5e330782e40","tid":1781153,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再講咩黎明行動無人<br />\n依家佢地已經變晒係便衣甴行咇<br />\n隨時出黎抓人堵路, 學有位巴打話<br />\n佢地一見到人, 基本上五分鍾左右就會到現場<br />\n佢地會自己抓幾個手足, 然後好快狗車就已經到<br />\n因為一早要CALL 左台, 再自己上去抓人立功<br />\n要再有行動一定要配合遊行同集會<br />\n而民陣遊行集會我覺得需要一個月或兩個月一次<br />\n而細遊行集會就一個月最少一次去MAKE NOISE<br />\n路程短小唔緊要, 最緊要比大家記番起同埋唔好麻木<br />\n<br />\n另外依家文宣嚴重不足同埋大洛後<br />\n要更加多創意同埋POST 宣傳<br />\n同埋區議會要開始聚人心幫助運動<br />\n建議18區係政事台開 長久POST 好似結衣BB 呢D 長期同一區討論活動<br />\n大家一齊18區 都會有區議會活動, 講座、播映會、討論、和你唱和你寫..."},{"pid":"ed598d89b3c8d8d938603e475c2bab149f8f93f4","tid":1781153,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g35FXT5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg35FXT5.gif&h=95e888ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"637f16b096a9772eeba54f721b4b5bd3a4b8e663","tid":1781153,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58NMTsC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58NMTsC.png&h=40618477&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3b17a1a40ac463c44cfd48e839a0a02bff1d2af","tid":1781153,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"和理非活動唔應該再局限於 愛丁堡集會"},{"pid":"c14219f85f65f3dbf8cf153c15cdae08e92f25cc","tid":1781153,"uid":29917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"秘密警察"},{"pid":"d9e44ac48edb960230fb097abfc595f69d1c9c83","tid":1781153,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor